, features a marbled bar and chartreuse velvet seating surrounding a custom walnut coffee table. Curved cove lighting and a vintage Italian resin lamp bring softness to the dramatic palette.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1459\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/living-room-purple-walls-210625-1049-01.jpg\" alt=\"This media room, painted in deep aubergine, features a marbled bar and chartreuse velvet seating surrounding a custom walnut coffee table. Curved cove lighting and a vintage Italian resin lamp bring softness to the dramatic palette.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/living-room-purple-walls-210625-1049-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/living-room-purple-walls-210625-1049-01-940x714.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/living-room-purple-walls-210625-1049-01-800x608.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/living-room-purple-walls-210625-1049-01-768x584.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/living-room-purple-walls-210625-1049-01-1536x1167.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1708\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/living-room-purple-walls-210625-1049-02.jpg\" alt=\"This media room, painted in deep aubergine, features a marbled bar and chartreuse velvet seating surrounding a custom walnut coffee table. Curved cove lighting and a vintage Italian resin lamp bring softness to the dramatic palette.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/living-room-purple-walls-210625-1049-02.jpg 1708w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/living-room-purple-walls-210625-1049-02-940x1409.jpg 940w, https://www.cont