personal touch.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1408\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-210625-1047-01.jpg\" alt=\"This primary suite is softened with plaster in a lavender-gray hue, complemented by stained oak elements. Custom floating nightstands are lit by printed linen sconces, and a vintage resin pendant hangs overhead. A framed still life adds a final personal touch.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-210625-1047-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-210625-1047-01-940x689.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-210625-1047-01-800x587.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-210625-1047-01-768x563.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-210625-1047-01-1536x1126.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1910\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-210625-1047-02.jpg\" alt=\"This primary suite is softened with plaster in a lavender-gray hue, complemented by stained oak elements. Custom floating nightstands are lit by printed linen sconces, and a vintage resin pendant hangs overhead. A framed still life adds a final personal touch.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-210625-1047-02.jpg 1910w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-210625-1047-02-940x1260.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-210625-1047-02-800x1072.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-210625-1047-02-768x1029.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-210625-1047-02-1146x1536.jpg 1146w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-210625-1047-02-1528x2048.jpg 1528w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1910px) 100vw, 1910px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe guest bedroom makes a bold statement with a green velvet bed set between custom travertine side tables, while artwork, a wool rug, and trio of clay pendants bring warmth and texture.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2203\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-green-bed-210625-1047-01.jpg\" alt=\"This guest bedroom makes a bold statement with a green velvet bed set between custom travertine side tables, while artwork, a wool rug, and trio of clay pendants bring warmth and texture.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-green-bed-210625-1047-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-green-bed-210625-1047-01-940x1079.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-green-bed-210625-1047-01-800x918.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-green-bed-210625-1047-01-768x881.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-green-bed-210625-1047-01-1339x1536.jpg 1339w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-green-bed-210625-1047-01-1785x2048.jpg 1785w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe home office is cloaked in deep forest green and features a custom tambour white oak desk. LED lighting and window illuminates the space, balancing moodiness with functionality.\u003c/p\u003e\