hile a freestanding tub sits beneath a steel casement window overlooking the garden and the wood vanity is topped with onyx.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/freestanding-bathtub-bathroom-design-210625-1050-01.jpg 1359w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/freestanding-bathtub-bathroom-design-210625-1050-01-940x1383.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/freestanding-bathtub-bathroom-design-210625-1050-01-800x1177.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/freestanding-bathtub-bathroom-design-210625-1050-01-768x1130.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/freestanding-bathtub-bathroom-design-210625-1050-01-1044x1536.jpg 1044w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1359px) 100vw, 1359px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2473\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/freestanding-bathtub-bathroom-design-210625-1050-02.jpg\" alt=\"This primary bathroom continues the lavender-gray plaster from the bedroom and elevates it with dramatic stone selections. Green onyx and rosa aurora macchia vecchia marble define the shower, while a freestanding tub sits beneath a steel casement window overlooking the garden and the wood vanity is topped with onyx.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/freestanding-bathtub-bathroom-design-210625-1050-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/freestanding-bathtub-bathroom-design-210625-1050-02-940x1211.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/freestanding-bathtub-bathroom-design-210625-1050-02-800x1030.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/freestanding-bathtub-bathroom-design-210625-1050-02-768x989.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/freestanding-bathtub-bathroom-design-210625-1050-02-1193x1536.jpg 1193w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/freestanding-bathtub-bathroom-design-210625-1050-02-1590x2048.jpg 1590w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2537\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/wood-vanity-bathroom-design-210625-1050-03.jpg\" alt=\"This primary bathroom continues the lavender-gray plaster from the bedroom and elevates it with dramatic stone selections. Green onyx and rosa aurora macchia vecchia marble define the shower, while a freestanding tub sits beneath a steel casement window overlooking the garden and the wood vanity is topped with onyx.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/wood-vanity-bathroom-design-210625-1050-03.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/wood-vanity-bathroom-design-210625-1050-03-940x1242.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/wood-vanity-bathroom-design-210625-1050-03-800x1057.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/wood-vanity-bathroom-design-210625-1050-03-768x1015.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/wood-vanity-bathroom-design-210625-1050-03-1162x1536.jpg 1162w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/wood-vanity-bathroom-design-210625-1050-03-1550x2048.jpg 1550w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eCompact yet luxurious, the powder room features creamy plaster walls and a sculptural Irish Connemara marble sink. A backlit asymmetrical mirror adds dimension and softness to the narrow space.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1676\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/powder-room-210625-1053-01.jpg\" alt=\"Compact yet luxurious, this powder room features creamy plaster walls and a sculptural Irish Connemara marble sink. A backlit asymmetrical mirror adds dimension and softness to the narrow space.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/powder-room-210625-1053-01.jpg 1676w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/powder-room-210625-1053-01-940x1436.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/powder-room-210625-1053-01-800x1222.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/powder-room-210625-1053-01-768x1173.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/powder-room-210625-1053-01-1006x1536.jpg 1006w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/powder-room-210625-1053-01-1341x2048.jpg 1341w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1676px) 100vw, 1676px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn the guest bath, espectaculo marble wraps both floor and walls, while rosa aurora stone tiles define the skylit tub and shower recess.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2400\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bathroom-210625-1057-01.jpg\" alt=\"In this guest bath, espectaculo marble wraps both floor and walls, while rosa aurora stone tiles define the skylit tub and shower recess.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bathroom-210625-1057-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bathroom-210625-1057-01-940x1175.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bathroom-210625-1057-01-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bathroom-210625-1057-01-768x960.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bathroom-210625-1057-01-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bathroom-210625-1057-01-1638x2048.jpg 1638w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe laundry space brings character to the utilitarian, with patterned cement tiles in a bold anarch design, tying into the home’s larger material story.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1764\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/colorful-laundry-room-210625-1048-01.jpg\" alt=\"This laundry space brings character to the utilitarian, with patterned cement tiles in a bold anarch design, tying into the home’s larger material story.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/colorful-laundry-room-210625-1048-01.jpg 1764w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/colorful-laundry-room-210625-1048-01-940x1364.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/colorful-laundry-room-210625-1048-01-800x1161.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/colorful-laundry-room-210625-1048-01-768x1115.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/colorful-laundry-room-210625-1048-01-1058x1536.jpg 1058w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/colorful-laundry-room-210625-1048-01-1411x2048.jpg 1411w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1764px) 100vw, 1764px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThroughout the townhouse, the thoughtful use of materials, form, and light supports both beauty and function, making this home not just a place to live, but a space to host, recharge, and create lasting memories.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.gievesanderson.com/\"\u003eGieves Anderson\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h6\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
